---
title: Griddled Onion Cheeseburgers with Special Sauce & Garlic Potato Wedges
description: Is there anything more satisfying than a cheeseburger? (Don’t worry, we checked, and the answer was a resounding “no!”) There is a difference, however, between a good cheeseburger and a great one. After you try a bite of ours, we know you’ll agree that this one falls in the GREAT category. Juicy beef patties are topped with melty cheddar, sweet griddled onion, ripe tomato slices, and finally, special sauce. We can’t give too much away, but what we *can* say is that the name is accurate. It’s creamy, tangy, savory, and well... pretty spesh! You’ll want to put it on everything, but it’s especially awesome on the side with these crispy potato wedges.
